<hs:element64>
Employment Opportunities
</hs:element64>
<hs:element70>
Hello and thank you for your interest in joining our team!
We are always looking for new smiling faces to join the West Orange Cinema family. West Orange Cinema has been family operated since 1989. Our goal is to provide our customers the best movie value and experience. We are looking for potential employees who are good team players, take initiative, and can provide quick and courteous service to our customers.
Please be aware we are open 365 days a year and are looking for employees available for weekends, holidays, and summertime. Pick up an application in our box office during our business hours at your earliest convenience or use the attached application below.
Sincerely,
West Orange Cinema Management
</hs:element70>
